    ğŸ”¹ `--target=file`      --> ğŸ¯ Specifies the name of the file where the image will be saved.
    ğŸ”¹ `--force-lba`        --> ğŸ’ª Forces the use of LBA (Logical Block Addressing) for addressing. (If necessary.)

ğŸ›  **Examples:**

    $ grub-ntldr-img --target=ntldr.img

